                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                            oc:textContent "The Grader reviews a transcript and output files, then determines whether each expectation passes or fails. Provide clear evidence for each judgment." ],
                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                            oc:textContent "You have two jobs: grade the outputs, and critique the evals themselves. A passing grade on a weak assertion is worse than useless — it creates false confidence. When you notice an assertion that's trivially satisfied, or an important outcome that no assertion checks, say so." ] ;
                    oc:sectionLevel 2 ;
                    oc:sectionOrder 1 ;
                    oc:sectionTitle "Role" ],
                [ a oc:Section ;
